---

<div class:list={["mt-16", align === "center" && "text-center"]}>
  <h1 class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight">
    <slot name="title">Inge Gatovsky</slot>
  </h1>
  <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600">
    <slot name="desc"> Awesome Personal Page </slot>
  </p>
</div>
